\par \tab \tab \tab \tab ctIRC\tab = 0
\par \tab \tab \tab \tab ctIRCX\tab = 1
\par 
\par \tab Notes:\tab \tab If a server is an IRCX server, the control automatically switches to the IRCX 
\par }\pard \fi720\li1440\nowidctlpar\adjustright {mode at connection time.
\par The ConnectionType property is accessible as soon as the
\par OnConnectionState(csConnected) event is fired after calling the Connect 
\par method or as soon as the OnConnectionState(csLogging) event is fired after 
\par calling the Login method.
\par 
\par }\pard \nowidctlpar\adjustright {\tab \tab \tab The property throws an error if the control is not connected to a server.
